p: ZIKV strain H/PF/2013 was provided by the US Centers for Disease Control and Prevention (CDC).[ 19] DENV WHO reference strains DENV1 West Pac 74, DENV2 S-16803, DENV3 CH54389 and DENV4 TVP-376 were obtained from Dr. Robert Putnak (Walter Reed Army Institute of Research). C6/36 and Vero cells were obtained from ATCC. Experiments using live virus were conducted under biosafety level 2 containment.
